      • commit

        protected final void commit()
                     throws java.io.IOException
        Description copied from class: POIXMLDocumentPart
        Save the content in the underlying package part. Default implementation is empty meaning that the package part is left unmodified.

        Sub-classes should override and add logic to marshal the "model" into Ooxml4J.

        For example, the code saving a generic XML entry may look as follows:

         protected void commit() throws IOException {
   PackagePart part = getPackagePart();
   OutputStream out = part.getOutputStream();
   XmlObject bean = getXmlBean(); //the "model" which holds changes in memory
   bean.save(out, DEFAULT_XML_OPTIONS);
   out.close();
 }
        (将内容保存在基础包部分中。默认实现为空，这意味着包部分保持未修改。子类应该重写并添加逻辑以将“模型”编入Ooxml 4J。例如，保存通用的HTML条目的代码可能如下所示：受保护的val commit（）引发IOResponse { PackagePart = getPackagePart（）; OutputStream out =部分.getOutputStream（）; DatabObserver bean = getDatabBean（）; //在内存中保存更改的“模型” bean.save，DID_XML_OPTIONS）; out.close（）; })
        Overrides:
        commit in class POIXMLDocumentPart
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - a subclass may throw an IOException if the changes can't be committed(java.io. IOResponse-如果无法提交更改，则子类别可能会引发IOResponse)

        Set the contents of this sheet to be a copy of the source sheet. This method erases any existing shapes and replaces them with object from the source sheet.(将此工作表的内容设置为源工作表的副本。此方法会擦除任何现有形状，并用源工作表中的对象替换它们。)
        Parameters:

      • getTheme

        public XSLFTheme getTheme()
        Returns:
        theme (shared styles) associated with this theme. By default returns null which means that this sheet is theme-less. Sheets that support the notion of themes (slides, masters, layouts, etc.) should override this method and return the corresponding package part.(与此主题关联的主题（共享样式）。默认情况下返回空，这意味着此工作表是无主题的。支持主题概念的工作表（幻灯片、母版、布局等）应该重写此方法并返回相应的包部件。)

      • getPlaceholderDetails

        public XSLFPlaceholderDetails getPlaceholderDetails(Placeholder placeholder)
        Description copied from interface: Sheet
        Get the placeholder details for the given placeholder type. Not all placeholders are also shapes - this is especially true for old HSLF slideshows, which notes have header/footers elements which aren't shapes.(获取给定占位符类型的占位符详细信息。并非所有占位符也是形状-对于旧的HSLF幻灯片显示尤其如此，其中的注释具有不是形状的标题/页脚元素。)
        Specified by:
        getPlaceholderDetails in interface Sheet<XSLFShape,XSLFTextParagraph>(接口中的getPlaceholderDetails Sheet)
        Parameters:
        placeholder - the placeholder type(占位符-占位符类型)
        Returns:
        the placeholder details or null, if the placeholder isn't contained in the sheet(如果占位符不包含在工作表中，则为空)
